videos.description: St. Mary's Calvin Hermanson drills the 3-pointer while getting fouled. He would hit the free throw to complete the 4-point play in the first half against Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Hermanson completes 4-point play for St. Mary's

videos.description: 1H (5:25) SMC Jordan Hunter made Layup. Assisted by Emmett Naar.
videos.headline: St Mary's uses the pick and roll for the layup

videos.description: Gonzaga's Johnathan Williams is the beneficiary of good Bulldogs' defense, and he finishes the play with a two-handed flush in the first half against St. Mary's.
videos.headline: Gonzaga gets the steal and Williams finishes with huge dunk

videos.description: Gonzaga's Zach Collins gets the ball down low and gets a layup to fall while getting fouled in the first half against St. Mary's.
videos.headline: Collins pumped for the and-1 opportunity

videos.description: 1H (1:08) GONZ Zach Collins made Layup. Assisted by Silas Melson.
videos.headline: Gonzaga gets the big block and it leads to basket on the other end
Big block by Gonzaga in final seconds of the 1st half

videos.description: Johnathan Williams protects the rim for Gonzaga swatting the layup out of bounds in the second half against St. Mary's.
videos.headline: Williams swats the shot out of bounds for Gonzaga

videos.description: Gonzaga guard Nigel Williams-Goss breaks down Gonzaga's 79-56 victory over St Mary's
videos.headline: Gonzaga guard Nigel Williams-Goss breaks down Gonzaga's 79-56 victory over St Mary's

videos.description: No. 5 Gonzaga pulls away from No. 21 Saint Mary's in the second half and improves to 17-0 on the season with a 79-56 victory.
videos.headline: Gonzaga makes statement with win over Saint Mary's
